Class WebSocketClientForLoRa

WebSocketClientForLoRa
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class WebSocketClientForLoRa
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.net.http.WebSocket.Listener

WEBSOCKET CLIENT

It implements functionality to receive data from the IoT board through the LoRaWAN network via websockets and send commands back to the LoRaWAN network
